# Utility Views

## Sessions
Purpose:
- let users revisit previous rehearsal sessions.

Possible content:
- session list
- date / title
- brief summary
- status
- link to review artifact

## Analytics
Purpose:
- provide supporting metrics and longitudinal feedback.

Possible content:
- delivery trends
- session frequency
- repeated failure points
- improvement over time

Important note:
- these are secondary views
- they should not interrupt the main Brief → Room → Debrief journey

